description: Lists configured table associations for a membership.

parameters.name: membershipIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the membership to list configured table associations for. Currently accepts the membership ID.

nested_items.name: configuredTableAssociationSummaries
nested_items.description: The retrieved list of configured table associations.

nested_items.name: configuredTableId
nested_items.description: The unique configured table ID that this configured table association refers to.

nested_items.name: membershipId
nested_items.description: The unique ID for the membership that the configured table association belongs to.

nested_items.name: membershipArn
nested_items.description: The unique ARN for the membership that the configured table association belongs to.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the configured table association. The table is identified by this name when running Protected Queries against the underlying data.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time the configured table association was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The time the configured table association was last updated.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The unique ID for the configured table association.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The unique ARN for the configured table association.

nested_items.name: analysisRuleTypes
nested_items.description: The analysis rule types that are associated with the configured table associations in this summary.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token that's used to fetch the next set of results.
